    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>Cajun-style spiced chicken thighs</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min on each side</p>",
