    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>grated garlic </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy garlic stock</strong></p>",
